  "title": "Social Worker/ Caseworker (Home)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assess the needs of seniors requiring care or services and develop care plans.</li>\n  <li>Assist in the creation and implementation of programs for seniors, including data collection and basic analysis.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate care for seniors with relevant stakeholders.</li>\n  <li>Document case notes.</li>\n  <li>Facilitate appropriate service referrals for seniors.</li>\n  <li>Participate in case discussions with external service providers.</li>\n  <li>Provide case management services.</li>\n  <li>Conduct needs assessments for seniors in the community.</li>\n  <li>Prepare data for submission to relevant authorities.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Social Work, Psychology, or Counselling</li>\n  <li>Preferably 1 of experience in the social service sector or a related field</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p><br></p>",
